---
title: Herby Beef & Pork Fusilli with Broccoli & Garden Salad
description: We love fusilli, it might be our favourite pasta shape! All those swirly twirly edges are perfect for catching whatever flavours you pair it with. Tonight, we’re tossing it through savoury beef & pork mince and vibrant green broccoli, with a simple sweet-and-tangy salad. Sounds like a perfect combo to us!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66ebb3d48e45e3ca0086301b-a88e0826.jpeg
